<risk_factor>None</risk_factor>
<script_version>1.30</script_version>
<see_also>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Session_Initiation_Protocol</see_also>
<solution>If possible, filter incoming connections to the port so that it is used only by trusted sources.</solution>
<synopsis>The remote system is a SIP signaling device.</synopsis>
<plugin_output>
The remote service was identified as :

  TANDBERG/4145 (X14.3.7)
</plugin_output>
</ReportItem>
