<risk_factor>None</risk_factor>
<script_version>1.2</script_version>
<see_also>https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6265</see_also>
<solution>Each cookie should be carefully reviewed to determine if it contains sensitive data or is relied upon for a security decision.

If needed, set an expiration date in the future so the cookie will persist or remove the Expires cookie attribute altogether to convert the cookie to a session cookie.</solution>
